{
  "stem": "12150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had enough food at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and we thought this may last, for a year or two, until the war is over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we didn't know what-- what's ahead of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day-- that was only after 10 days, or 12, approximately.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We found out that every day-- heard big loudspeakers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every day, around a certain time-- maybe 5:00 PM-- about 800 people, 800 names, will be called to report early in the morning, with their belongings, to a certain place in the ghetto area.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wasn't one of the first ones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- they said it's for resettlement-- official-- official declaration resettlement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know what it means-- concentration camps, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Resettlement-- we already knew it's not-- it's not good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we hoped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody hoped, maybe, by a miracle, he'll survive, somehow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So every day they-- around 800 people had to report in the morning-- I don't remember exactly-- to a certain area in the ghetto, surrounded by police, and SS guards.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they read off the names, and lists, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after a while, they marched to a railroad station, a railroad track.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we didn't know-- while we were in the ghetto, we don't know where they were marched.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because the Germans managed to do everything in secret.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were masters at it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So one day, was-- my name was called.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I took my little belongings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was one suitcase, one bag, or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I reported like the others.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and then-- Excuse me, Harry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "How many people were living in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Do you have any idea?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say 10,000.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "About 10,000 people, or maybe more, not less-- spread out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a tremendous area.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
